Historical Statement:
---------------------
This license aims to carve into history the crimes committed by regular Russian people in Ukraine, including but not limited to:

- spooked to protest, bold to seize
- rape, including forcing parents to watch as their children were raped
- various and systematic tortures of the occupied population
- torturing prisoners of war
- mutilation
- mining corpses after torture to prevent burial
- mass murder and executions of civilians
- abduction of children
- deliberate bombing of civilian infrastructure (schools, hospitals, energy facilities, etc.)
- erasure of Ukrainian heritage
- looting toilets














